description: This file defines Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) related to friend requests and friend entries within a social application backend. It contains class definitions for creating a friend request, representing friend request responses, and representing a friend entry in a list.

classes.name: FriendRequestCreate
classes.description: DTO for creating a friend request, specifies the recipient user ID.

classes.name: FriendRequestResponse
classes.description: DTO representing a friend request with status, IDs, timestamps.

classes.name: FriendEntry
classes.description: DTO representing a friend in a list with user ID, username, and optional display name.
